refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public voidDs\Seq::unshift mixedvalues
Adds values to the front of the seq, moving all current values forward to make room for the new values.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Ds\Seq::unshift example


<?php
$seq = new \Ds\Seq([1, 2, 3]);

$seq->unshift("a");
print_r($seq);

$seq->unshift("x", "y");
print_r($seq);
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


Ds\Seq Object
(
    [0] => a
    [1] => 1
    [2] => 2
    [3] => 3
)
Ds\Seq Object
(
    [0] => x
    [1] => y
    [2] => a
    [3] => 1
    [4] => 2
    [5] => 3
)
